IMAPStore proton-remote
Host 127.0.0.1
Port 1143
User skh@saianeesh.com 
PassCmd "pass mutt-wizard-proton"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType None
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore proton-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/proton/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/proton/INBOX
Flatten .

Channel proton
Expunge Both
Far :proton-remote:
Near :proton-local:
Patterns * !"All Mail"
Create Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0
ExpireUnread no
# End profile

IMAPStore jhu-remote
Host outlook.office365.com 
Port 993
User sharida2@alumni.jh.edu
PassCmd "oauth2ms"
AuthMechs XOAUTH2
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersion TLSv1.2
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
PipelineDepth 50

MaildirStore jhu-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/jhu/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/jhu/INBOX
Flatten .

Channel jhu
Expunge Both
Far :jhu-remote:
Near :jhu-local:
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail" !Calendar* !Notes !Clutter !Contacts !"Conversation History" !Journal !Tasks !Outbox !Scheduled 
Create Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0
ExpireUnread no
# End profile

